## 1. Definitions

“Software” means the WHA Magic project and all original files distributed with it.

“Unmodified Software” means an official compiled release of the Software distributed by Maxello1 that has not been altered, patched, decompiled, recompiled, or otherwise modified.

“Server” means a Minecraft server, including a private, public, community, or commercial Minecraft server.

“Modpack” means a collection of Minecraft mods distributed together without modifying the contents of the individual WHA Magic JAR file.

