You are granted a limited, non-exclusive, revocable, non-transferable license to:

a. download and run the Unmodified Software;

b. install and use the Unmodified Software on Minecraft clients and Servers;

c. use the Unmodified Software on private, public, community, or commercial Minecraft Servers;

d. include and redistribute the unmodified official WHA Magic JAR file as part of a Minecraft modpack, provided that:

* the WHA Magic JAR remains completely unmodified;
* this license and all copyright notices remain intact;
* the project is not represented as being created, maintained, or endorsed by anyone other than its actual authors;
* recipients are provided with a link or clear reference to the official WHA Magic project page;

e. combine the Unmodified Software with other independently developed Minecraft mods, plugins, datapacks, resource packs, server configurations, scripts, or modpack content;

f. create and distribute configuration files, datapacks, resource packs, compatibility data, or other external content that interacts with the Software through its publicly supported configuration or integration systems, provided that such content does not contain copied source code, modified Software files, or a modified WHA Magic JAR.

